############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION Take the coefficient of [`x^2`] for the value of [`a\text{,}`] the coefficient of [`x`] for [`b\text{,}`] and the constant for [`c\text{.}`] _In this case_, they are [`a = 2\text{,}`] [`b = -7\text{,}`] [`c = -15\text{.}`]
END_PGML_SOLUTION
